\begin_body

\begin_layout Section
换元法和分部积分法
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proposition
(常见函数的积分)常见函数有以下的积分表: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\int\tan x\dd x=-\ln|\cos x|+C\qquad & \int\cot x\dd x=\ln|\sin x|+C\\
\int\sec x\dd x=\ln|\tan x+\sec x|+C\qquad & \int\csc x\dd x=\ln|\csc x-\cot x|+C\\
\int\frac{1}{1+x^{2}}\dd x=\arctan x+C\qquad & \int\frac{1}{1-x^{2}}\dd x=\ln\left|\frac{x+1}{x-1}\right|+C\\
\int\sqrt{1-x^{2}}\dd x=\frac{x}{2}\sqrt{1-x^{2}}+\frac{1}{2}\arcsin x+C\qquad & \int\sqrt{x^{2}\pm1}\dd x=\frac{x}{2}\sqrt{x^{2}\pm1}+\frac{1}{2}\ln|x+\sqrt{x^{2}\pm1}+C
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Problem
求解
\begin_inset Formula $I_{n}=\int f_{n}(x)\dd x,f_{n}(x)=\frac{1}{(x^{2}+1)^{n}}$
\end_inset

以及
\begin_inset Formula $f_{n}(x)=\sin^{n}x$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
几类初等函数的积分
\end_layout

\begin_layout Problem
已知: 在复数域上一切实系数多项式都可以分解成若干个一次因式的乘积, 证明: 一个有理真分式一定可以表示成若干个最简分式的和, 而最简真分式有且仅有如下四种:
 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{A}{x-a},\frac{A}{(x-a)^{m}},\frac{Mx+N}{x^{2}+px+q}(p^{2}-4q<0),\frac{Mx+N}{(x^{2}+px+q)^{k}}(k>1,p^{2}-4q<0).
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Problem
并且将
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{2x+2}{x^{5}-x^{4}+2x^{3}-2x^{2}+x-1}$
\end_inset

化为上述形式.
 
\end_layout

